## 1. Pre-Deployment Checks

### 1.1 Static Analysis

#### Slither (Trail of Bits)

```bash
# Installation
pip install slither-analyzer

# Run full analysis
slither contracts/ --solc-remaps @openzeppelin/=$(pwd)/node_modules/@openzeppelin/ --exclude-informational --exclude-low --json slither-report.json

# Check for specific detectors
slither contracts/ --detect reentrancy-eth,reentrancy-benign,reentrancy-events,unchecked-transfer,unchecked-lowlevel,delegatecall-loop,msg-value-loop,assembly-usage,suicidal,uninitialized-state,uninitialized-storage,uninitialized-local,shadowing-local,shadowing-abstract,shadowing-state,arbitrary-send-eth,weak-prng,controlled-delegatecall,controlled-array-length,write-after-write,variable-scope,void-cst,incorrect-shift,incorrect-exp
```

